POST懶人包</span></strong><br />\n<blockquote><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1458355/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1458355/page/1</a><br />\n我係空管主任，我想講今日機場真係呢兩個幾月黎香港人贏得最靚既一仗<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1458321/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1458321/page/1</a><br />\n有消息嘗試用舉牌方式同人講<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1457623/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1457623/page/1</a><br />\n我覺得今日散水無錯，互屌先係真中計<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1457903/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1457903/page/1</a><br />\n[賽後檢討] 今日機場有無散水既都麻煩入一入黎<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1457735/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1457735/page/1</a><br />\n下次搞再機場唔該幫下啲旅客<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1457517/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1457517/page/1</a><br />\n今日機場事件有少少諗法<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1457187/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1457187/page/1</a><br />\n我係散水撚，我係嚟道歉嘅</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好需要你幫手報料/update/宣傳呀"},{"pid":"29304f379fed86bdddbaed1f53557b30b5798164","tid":1458574,"uid":275577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:54:24.000Z","msg":"試下無妨"},{"pid":"bd0b82a62c48303b443ffc436d00b2bc96802796","tid":1458574,"uid":64744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:59:18.000Z","msg":"推下"},{"pid":"015259fefaa9c7165d1d5a117db96774cd9bc8b6","tid":1458574,"uid":161410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f7ef1ca9704a447dd1043b5d1798215d4ece5ac","tid":1458574,"uid":64744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1bbed28a8e0ad4431a1af54b42a0028d453da67","tid":1458574,"uid":161410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b145f52cca39e6a5ebef95488ab20b380a65d8